{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"893ac80255","title":"四兵团应乘胜追击占领高要德庆等县","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"017f5e19b3","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":17,"articleId":"893ac80255"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"d019d3a3f2","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任第四野战军兼华中军区司令员。"},{"id":"246be07bcf","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记、广东军区司今员兼政治委员。陈唐，当时任第二野战军第四兵团司令员兼政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"29bc7f4a03","type":"title","text":"四兵团应乘胜追术占领高要德庆等具","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255"},{"id":"d019d3a3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪呵志，并告剑英、陈质","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255"},{"id":"246be07bcf","type":"paragraph","text":"广州敌逃跑方向，不是向正西入广西就是向西南入海南岛。我四兵团似应乘胜追击，直至占高要、德庆、封川、高明、新兴、云浮、郁南、罗定等县，必要时并占领梧州，然后停下来休整待命，听候你的统一部署入桂作战。因为占领上述诸县，一则可能歼灭逃故一部或大部，使十五兵团易于攻取海南岛，消灭残敌，平定全粤；二则即是对于入桂作战完成了部队的展开。是否可以这样做，请按情况的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255"},{"id":"d2e18ea0b6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255"},{"id":"23f19639df","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255"}],"page":{"id":"e38c9a6873","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"893ac80255","start":431,"end":431}}}},"__N_SSG":true}